Executive Profile
Anahaita N. Kotval  Independent Director, OneMain Holdings, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 3 Board Members in 3 different organizations across 3 different industries.See Board Relationships50$130,000
Background

		Ms. Anahaita N. Kotval has been the Chief Operating Officer and General Counsel at Inspirica, Inc. since November 2011. Ms. Kotval served in various positions with RBS Securities Inc. , a U.S. broker-dealer and affiliate of the Royal Bank of Scotland, including serving as its General Counsel from 2007 to October 2011, Deputy General Counsel from 2004 to 2007 and Associate General Counsel from 1998 to 2004. She spent 5 years in the Enforcement Division of the U.S. Securities ... and Exchange Commission’s New York Regional Office. She has been a Director of OneMain Holdings, Inc. (formerly, Springleaf Holdings, Inc.) since December 19, 2012. She holds a B.Sc. from Brown University in Applied Mathematics and Economics and a J.D. from Harvard Law School.Read Full Background




