Insider Activity


Individual




Anahaita N. Kotval



Ms. Anahaita N. Kotval is Chief Operating Officer & General Counsel at Inspirica, Inc. She is on the Board of Directors at Springleaf Finance Corp., Springleaf Finance, Inc., My Sisters Place, Inc. and OneMain Holdings, Inc. Ms. Kotval was previously employed as General Counsel by RBS Securities, Inc. and a Principal by US Securities & Exchange Commission.



